《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》是由[[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]担纲导演及编剧的美国[[科幻电影|科幻电影]]，由[[二十世纪福斯|二十世纪福斯]]发行，2009年上映。影片于2009年12月10日在英国伦敦首映，12月18日登陆北美，上映首日票房高达高达2700万美元，首周末于3461家影院上映，票房累计达7700万美元，位列票房榜首位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=avatar.htm|title=Avatar (2009) – Weekend Box Office Results|access-date=2010-02-02|publisher=Box Office Mojo|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023173250/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=avatar.htm|archive-date=2013-10-23}}</ref>。凭借27亿美元的全球票房，影片是目前[[全球最高電影票房收入列表|全球票房成绩最高的电影]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |title=‘Avatar’ Overtakes ‘Avengers: Endgame’ As All-Time Highest-Grossing Film At Global Box Office; China Reissue Growing |url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/avatar-overtakes-avengers-endgame-highest-grossing-film-all-time-worldwide-box-office-china-james-cameron-disney-1234713788/ |website=Deadline |accessdate=2021-03-13 |date=2021-03-13}}</ref>，仅次于2019年的《[[復仇者聯盟：終局之戰|復仇者聯盟：終局之戰]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1432421380/|title='The Lion King' Debuts with Record $185M & 'Endgame' Becomes Global #1|publisher=Box Office Mojo|access-date=2020-09-15|date=2019-07-21|last=Brevet|first=Brad|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914142901/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4530|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同时也是[[美國和加拿大最高電影票房收入列表|北美票房收入最高的电影]]，直至2016年被《[[STAR_WARS：原力覺醒|STAR WARS：原力覺醒]]》超越<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4142&p=.htm|title='Star Wars: Force Awakens' Becomes Highest Grossing Domestic Release of All-Time|publisher=Box Office Mojo|access-date=2017-04-14|date=2016-01-07|last=Brevet|first=Brad|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415081501/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4142&p=.htm|archive-date=2017-04-15}}</ref>，是首部全球票房突破20亿美元的电影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=9711561|title='Avatar' Wins Box Office, Nears Domestic Record|access-date=2010-02-02|publisher=ABC News|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203052551/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=9711561|archive-date=2010-02-03}}</ref>。在汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]，影片获得83%的新鲜度<ref name="rottentomatoes">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avatar/|title=Avatar|publisher=Flixster|work=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2010-02-02|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231002453/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/avatar/|archive-date=2010-12-31}}</ref>。

影片在[[第82届奥斯卡金像奖|第82届奥斯卡金像奖]]赢得[[奥斯卡最佳艺术指导奖|最佳艺术指导]]、[[奧斯卡最佳攝影獎|最佳攝影]]及[[奧斯卡最佳視覺效果獎|最佳視覺效果]]三项大奖，获[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳导演|最佳导演]]等九项提名<ref name="oscar">{{cite web|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|title=The 82nd Academy Awards (2010) Nominees and Winners|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html|access-date=2012-08-22|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006110009/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/82nd-winners.html|archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>；获[[第67届金球奖|第67届金球奖]][[金球獎最佳戲劇類影片|最佳剧情片]]及[[金球獎最佳導演|最佳导演]]<ref name="globe">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbc.com/golden-globes/nominees/|title=The Golden Globe Awards 2010 Nominees|publisher=NBC|access-date=2010-01-14|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100709151559/http://www.nbc.com/golden-globes/nominees/|archive-date=2010-07-09}}</ref>；获[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]八项提名，赢得{{tsl|en|BAFTA Award for Best Production Design|英国电影学院奖最佳艺术指导奖|最佳艺术指导}}和{{tsl|en|BAFTA Award for Best Special Visual Effects|英国电影学院奖最佳视觉效果|最佳视觉效果}}；获{{tsl|en|Visual Effects Society|视觉效果工会奖}}六项大奖；获{{tsl|en|36th Saturn Awards|第36届土星奖}}十项提名，其中[[佐伊·索尔达娜|佐伊·索尔达娜]]赢得[[土星獎最佳電影女主角|最佳电影女主角]]<ref name="saturn">{{cite news|first=David S.|last=Cohen|url=https://www.variety.com/article/VR1118021047.html?categoryid=14&cs=1&ref=bd_tv|title=Saturn Awards open Pandora's box |work=Variety|date=2010-06-24 |access-date=2010-06-24}}</ref>。另外，影片还获[[美国导演工会奖|美国导演工会奖]]、{{tsl|en|Producers Guild of America Awards|美国制片人工会奖}}和[[美国编剧工会奖|美国编剧工会奖]]的提名。

影片获得北美众多影评人协会的认可，获[[评论家选择电影奖|评论家选择电影奖]]九项提名，赢得最佳动作电影及其他技术类奖<ref name="bfca">{{cite web|url=http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2009.php|title=The 15th Critics' Choice Awards Nominees|publisher=Broadcast Film Critics Association|access-date=2010-03-08|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217044040/http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2009.php|archive-date=2013-02-17}}</ref>；获[[奥斯汀影评人协会|奥斯汀影评人协会]]和[[达拉斯—沃斯堡影评人协会|达拉斯—沃斯堡影评人协会]]列入年度十佳电影榜单<ref>{{cite web |last1=Robinson |first1=Anna |title=Surprise Win x3 from France + Second Consecutive ‘Gay’ Best Actor: Awards Season |url=https://www.altfg.com/film/surprise-win/ |website=Alt Film Guide |accessdate=2021-03-11 |date=2009-12-15 |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311083247/https://www.altfg.com/film/surprise-win/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Wilonsky|first=Robert|date=2009-12-16|url=http://blogs.dallasobserver.com/unfairpark/2009/12/dfw_crix_up_in_the_air_with_ye.php|title=DFW Crix ''Up in the Air'' With Year-End Tally|work=Dallas Observer|access-date=2010-04-07|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322075509/http://blogs.dallasobserver.com/unfairpark/2009/12/dfw_crix_up_in_the_air_with_ye.php|archive-date=2014-03-22}}</ref>；获凤凰城影评人协会最佳摄影、最佳剪辑、最佳艺术指导、最佳视觉效果奖，入选年度十佳电影榜单<ref>{{cite web |last=Boyd |first=Colin |date=2009-12-22 |url=http://www.getthebigpicture.net/blog/2009/12/22/basterds-dominates-phoenix-film-critics-awards.html |title='Basterds' Dominates Phoenix Film Critics Awards |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100110153716/http://www.getthebigpicture.net/blog/2009/12/22/basterds-dominates-phoenix-film-critics-awards.html |archivedate=2010-01-10 |website=Get the Big Picture |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2021-03-11 }}</ref>；获[[圣路易斯影评人协会|圣路易斯影评人协会]]最佳视觉效果、最具创新性影片奖<ref>{{cite web |last1=Montgomery |first1=Steve |title=Christoph Waltz + Mo’Nique: Critics Awards’ Clean Sweep |url=https://www.altfg.com/film/christoph-waltz-monique/ |website=Alt Film Guide |date=2009-12-21 |accessdate=2021-03-11 |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311083247/https://www.altfg.com/film/christoph-waltz-monique/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；获[[纽约在线影评人协会|纽约在线影评人协会]]最佳影片奖<ref>{{cite news|last=Davis|first=Don|date=2009-12-14|url=https://www.variety.com/article/VR1118012762.html?categoryId=13&cs=1|title=N.Y. Online Critics like 'Avatar'|work=Variety|access-date=2009-12-15}}</ref>。

2009年12月，[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]将影片列入“AFI年度重要时刻”，表彰卡梅隆推动[[计算机成像|计算机成像]]发展，认为影片“会对艺术形式日后的发展产生深远影响”<ref>{{cite web|title=AFI Moments Of Significance|date=December 2009|publisher=American Film Institute|url=http://www.afi.com/tvevents/afiawards/moments.aspx|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091217194857/http://www.afi.com/tvevents/afiawards/moments.aspx|archive-date=2009-12-17|accessdate=2021-03-11}}</ref>。2010年1月，中华人民共和国[[湖南省|湖南省]][[张家界市|张家界市]]政府决定将[[张家界国家森林公园|张家界国家-{森}-林公园]]中一座{{convert|3544|ft}}高的[[石英|石英]][[砂岩|砂岩]]山，更名为[[阿凡达-哈利路亚山|阿凡达-哈利路亚山]]，纪念这部电影<ref>{{cite web|title="Avatar" inspires China province to rename mountain|date=2010-01-26|work=China Daily|url=http://www2.chinadaily.com.cn/life/2010-01/26/content_9375209.htm|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606043905/http://www2.chinadaily.com.cn/life/2010-01/26/content_9375209.htm|archive-date=2011-06-06|accessdate=2021-03-11}}</ref>。《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》将影片列入“10部具里程碑意义的电影”榜单<ref>{{cite news | first = Richard | last = Corliss | title = The 10 Greatest Movies of the Millennium (Thus Far) | work = Time | url = http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/17/top-10-movies-of-the-millennium/#avatar-2009-u-s | date = 2012-05-17 | access-date = 2012-05-21 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120521050843/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/17/top-10-movies-of-the-millennium/#avatar-2009-u-s | archive-date = 2012-05-21 }}</ref>及{{le|时代百大电影|Time's All-TIME 100 Movies}}榜单<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/17/movie-masterpieces-richard-corliss-expands-times-list-of-cinematic-greats/#avatar|title=Rethinking the Movie Masterpieces: Richard Corliss Expands TIME's List of Cinematic Greats|work=Time|first=Richard|last=Corliss|date=2012-05-17|access-date=2012-05-21|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520081905/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/17/movie-masterpieces-richard-corliss-expands-times-list-of-cinematic-greats/#avatar|archive-date=2012-05-20}}</ref>；[[IGN|IGN]]将影片列入史上25大科幻电影榜的第22位<ref>{{cite web | url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/677/677739p1.html | title=Top 25 Sci-Fi Movies of All Time | work=IGN | date=2010-09-17 | access-date=2010-11-28 | dead-url=no | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101204000706/http://movies.ign.com/articles/677/677739p1.html | archive-date=2010-12-04 }}</ref>。

